And she gave them a normal eyesight chart,
给他们一幅普通的视力表

1427
01:14:38,700 --> 01:14:41,970
measured them, wrote down their performance.
测量他们的视力 记录结果

1428
01:14:41,970 --> 01:14:44,570
And then she took the exact same people--
然后她把让同一群人

1429
01:14:44,920 --> 01:14:48,490
this time, put them in a pilot overalls
这次让他们穿上飞行服

1430
