Same distance, same eye chart,
相同的距离 相同的视力表

1433
01:15:01,410 --> 01:15:04,890
the only difference being they're sitting in a flight simulator
唯一的不同是 他们坐在

1434
01:15:05,210 --> 01:15:08,650
and they were wearing pilot overalls.
飞行模拟器里 穿着飞行服

1435
01:15:08,650 --> 01:15:14,140
They were sitting there, looking at the eye chart.
他们坐在那里看视力表

1436
01:15:14,140 --> 01:15:16,380
And again, she ran the eye test.
然后她又进行了一次视力测试

1437
01:15:16,980 --> 01:15:21,650
40% of participants eyesight improved significantly,
40%的参与者的视力有明显改善

1438
