is how can we create consciously
如何创造有意识的

1487
01:18:21,800 --> 01:18:25,300
and subconsciously a positive environment
和潜意识的积极环境

1488
01:18:26,260 --> 01:18:30,390
where we actually can take out the most moral,
让我们带出最有道德

1489
01:18:30,890 --> 01:18:34,370
most successful self, to appreciate that self,
最成功的自我 并且去欣赏那个自我

1490
01:18:34,370 --> 01:18:37,430
to help the environment bring out the best in us.
帮助环境带出最杰出的自己

